claim.claim-text:
1. A lawn mower guard device, comprising: 
a mounting plate having an outer surface and an inner surface; 
a bristled member; 
a first hook and loop fastener carried by said outer surface of said mounting plate; 
a second hook and loop fastener having an exposed surface and a rear surface, said bristled member carried by said rear surface and said exposed surface removably secured to said outer surface of said mounting plate; and 
at least one magnet carried on said inner surface of said mounting plate.
